OL,7,FRobbers attacked a person attending ,
OL,8,Fstealing an flag and their wallet,
OL,9,Fbefore spending their money in
OL,10,FMcDonald's.
OL,12,FCallum Lewis, 22, and Melanie Shaw
OL,13,F(also known as Price), 28, stole from
OL,14,Fthe victim in city centre at roughly
OL,15,F3:30am on August 28 2022.
OL,17,Fheard the victim, who had just left
OL,18,FHeidi's bar on Mill Lane, was seen on
OL,19,FCCTV talking to Lewis and a woman sat
OL,20,Fon a bench before Shaw later arrived
OL,21,Fand joined the group.
