OL,7,FThe victim, who was walking along St
OL,8,FMary Street wearing a rainbow-coloured
OL,9,Fflag around their shoulders, was then
OL,10,Fpushed to the floor by Shaw.
OL,12,FAfter Shaw took the flag, they were
OL,13,Fthen pushed to the floor again as they
OL,14,Ftried to get it back.
OL,16,FThey were then pushed to the floor for
OL,17,Fa third time and pulled along the
OL,18,Ffloor, causing grazes and marks to
OL,19,Ftheir left elbow.
