OL,7,FThe court heard the victim offered to
OL,8,Fgive the attackers their wallet to try
OL,9,Fto get them to leave them alone. Lewis
OL,10,Fasked for their pin number, which they
OL,11,Fgave out of fear.
OL,13,FThe next thing the victim remembered
OL,14,Fwas lying on the floor and trying to
OL,15,Fuse their phone, which had run out of
OL,16,Fbattery, before they saw a friend who
OL,17,Fhelped them home.
OL,19,FThey realised the next several
OL,20,Ftransactions had been made using their
OL,21,Fcard, mostly at McDonald's.
