OL,7,FThey added: "I am thinking about
OL,8,Fthings and what has happened to me and
OL,9,FI'm constantly worrying. This incident
OL,10,Fmade me feel so overwhelmed and I
OL,11,Fdidn't know how to cope. I had a Pride
OL,12,Fflag with me and looking at it was a
OL,13,Fconstant reminder and made me feel
OL,14,Funsafe in my own room.
OL,16,F"I am also worried about friends,
OL,17,Ffamily, and my partner. I am worried
OL,18,Fsomething might happen to them similar
OL,19,Fto what happened to me."
