OL,7,FShaw's barrister, Bethan Evans said
OL,8,Fher behaviour was caused by alcohol.
OL,9,FShe said Shaw had previously been a
OL,10,Fvictim of domestic abuse, and was
OL,11,Fstruggling with the news that her
OL,12,Fgrandmother had been diagnosed with
OL,13,Fcancer. The court heard that the
OL,14,Fmother of two is pregnant.
OL,16,FRecorder John Philpotts said there was
OL,17,Fno suggestion the robbery was
OL,18,Fmotivated by homophobia. He sentenced
OL,19,Fboth Lewis and Shaw to 18 months
OL,20,Fimprisonment each.
